plot: Lex proceeds to lay an intricate plan to bring Lena closer to him, defeat Leviathan's latest attack, and pit Supergirl against Leviathan; how Lex came into power after Crisis is revealed.

Lex's plans since Crisis and his emergence as a hero on the new Earth are revealed, as he secretly manipulates Lena, Supergirl, Eve, and Leviathan against each other to undermine Leviathan and bring about the death of the Kryptonians that he hates.—Gislef
